ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR NASA DATA USE

This software retrieves and processes data from NASA's Open Science Data
Repository (OSDR). Users of this software are responsible for:

1. Complying with NASA's data use policies
2. Appropriately citing original OSDR studies in publications
3. Acknowledging NASA GeneLab as the data source

Original study data is available at: https://osdr.nasa.gov/

